وصف باسم راهب دير طور سيناء المقدسة وهو برس نفسه وقلايته كتب في طور سيناء المقدسة وكان الفراغ منه نهار الثلثة العاشر من شهر اب سنة ستالاف وتسعمائه [ثلثة] تسعين لكون العالم والسبح لله دائما","translation":["It was copied at Holy Mount Si[nai?] Monastery during the day of Tuesday 10 in the month of Āb [August] in the Year of the Existence of the World [Anno Mundi] 6993"],"assoc_place":[{"value":"Holy Mount Si[nai?] Monastery","event":{"id":"origin","label":"Place of Origin"}}],"assoc_date":[{"value":"13 Ab 6993","type":{"id":"origin","label":"Date of Origin"}}]},{"type":{"id":"colophon","label":"Colophon"},"locus":"f. 239v ","lang":[{"id":"arab1395","label":"Arabic"}],"as_written":"نجز هذا الكتاب المبارك بعون الله تأييده وله السبح الله دائما لله المجد لله دائما / الحقير في / رؤسا الاهية فلان خادم لرئيس / فلان [الحقير] الرؤسا الاهية / والفلان حاكم لرئيس فلان / وأكتب ويقين عقلي يوم ؟ انا الحقير المسكين في رهبان طور سيناء الراهب يوصف","note":["Attested places:  Mount Sinai"]}],"assoc_date":[{"value":"1485 CE","iso":{"not_before":"1485"},"type":{"id":"origin","label":"Date of Origin"}}],"assoc_place":[{"value":"Holy Mount Si[nai?] Monastery (f. 1r)","event":{"id":"origin","label":"Place of Origin"},"note":["F. 1r"]}],"features":[{"id":"deco-geometric","label":"Decoration, Geometric"},{"id":"colophon","label":"Colophon"},{"id":"dated","label":"Dated"}],"note":[{"type":{"id":"ornamentation","label":"Ornamentation Note"},"value":"Geometric decoration on f. 1r, rosette with pattern in red and black ink"},{"type":{"id":"general","label":"Other Notes"},"value":"The beginning of f. 1v (2 and 1/4 lines) copied on f. 17r and then crossed out with red ink"}],"parent":["ark:/21198/z1d51rb9"]}]}],"location":[{"id":"sinai-oc","collection":"Old Collection","repository":"St. Catherine's Monastery of the Sinai"}],"note":[{"type":{"id":"para","label":"Paracontent Note"},"value":"Supplicant inscriptions, etc. ff. 1r, 59v, 99r, 239r, 239v, back board inside"}],"bib":[{"id":"deb668b6-feec-48